<plot>A musical short, with some trick photography, with Enric Madriguera and his Orchestra play. Patricia Gilmore sings "Maria from Bahia" and "Take it Away", and Acrobat dancers Shayne &amp; Armstrong do their bit. It ends with Eddie Gomez on a song while Lazara does a torrid native dance. This short was reissued on August 10, 1946.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?179060</url></doc>
